text: Tsai Wen-yee () is a Taiwanese weightlifter. He won a Bronze medal in the 60 kg class at the 1984 Summer Olympics in Los Angeles. == References == Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic weightlifters of Taiwan Category:Weightlifters at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Weightlifters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Taiwan Category:Olympic medalists in weightlifting Category:Medalists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Taiwanese male weightlifters
